data("EuStockMarkets")
Prices<-as.data.frame(EuStockMarkets)
T = dim(Prices)[1]
Returns<-log(Prices[2:T,]/Prices[1:T-1,])
reg1<-lm(DAX~CAC,Returns) #Run Regression
#par(mfrow=c(3,2))
plot(reg1,which=c(1))

plot(reg1,which=c(2))

plot(reg1,which=c(3))

plot(reg1,which=c(4))

plot(reg1,which=c(5))

plot(reg1,which=c(6))
